{"tid":2206362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國男子一次娶雙胞胎姐妹 ，盡享齊人之福 …","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:52:43.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e57acf98a867bed3a963040a50fa0358d984081","tid":2206362,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/mstory.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A8%B6%E9%9B%99%E8%83%9E%E8%83%8E%E5%A7%90%E5%A6%B9-%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%A1%E4%BA%AB%E9%BD%8A%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%8B%E7%A6%8F.jpg?resize=640%2C360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fmstory.me%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%25A8%25B6%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%2583%259E%25E8%2583%258E%25E5%25A7%2590%25E5%25A6%25B9-%25EF%25BC%258C%25E7%259B%25A1%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E9%25BD%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25A6%258F.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C360&h=4777d890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋覓理想的結婚伴侶並不易，泰國一名男子與一對?I生姐妹拍拖，然而他卻決定不了該跟誰結婚，結果索性把她們雙雙娶回家，盡享齊人之福。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n該名福無邊姓杜的男子（Winchao Tao）來自夜功府（SamutSongkram），與?I生姐妹青梅竹馬，經常形影不離，長大後連拍拖都一起。福男很想成家立室，只是無法決定最愛是誰，結果膽粗粗同時向兩女求婚，豈料她們一口答應，只是各要求122克黃金及1.9萬港元禮金作嫁妝。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n婚後姐妹花入住男家，各獲配一間睡房，而在新婚夜，她們各陪丈夫一晚，至第三晚才三人同眠。"},{"pid":"ae1f3dfa6137fd3b87f3f920ab64e8d2345b2d4b","tid":2206362,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e57acf98a867bed3a963040a50fa0358d984081","tid":2206362,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/mstory.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A8%B6%E9%9B%99%E8%83%9E%E8%83%8E%E5%A7%90%E5%A6%B9-%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%A1%E4%BA%AB%E9%BD%8A%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%8B%E7%A6%8F.jpg?resize=640%2C360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i